<TITLE> RAB busts haul of porn CDs in Savar </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Dhaka, Jan 27 (bdnews24.com)The Rapid Action Battalion has seized a huge haul of porn movies from a house in Savar in an overnight drive, officers said Sunday. The elite force also busted computers, copying devices, sound systems and 10 machines to make discs. RAB also arrested two alleged drug peddlers Saturday night: Suruj Miah, 28, and Helal Uddin, 34, and seized 20 grams of heroin from them in Genda area of Savar. In another drive Sunday, 27-year-old Sanowar Hossain was arrested by RAB with Phensydyl, a banned cough syrup used for intoxication. RAB-4 officer Ariful Islam told bdnews24.com that the gang had been involved in supplying porn CDs for long. The officer said one Aktar had earlier been arrested in Chapain area with links to the peddling of porn CDs. After searching his house, RAB found a small plant to copy CDs for sale. bdnews24.com
